~ Girl
Why are you crying?
Sarah: My paper recycling bin got knocked over by an animal
It might have been my dog, sorry. Have you seen where it went?
Sarah: I'll tell you where it went after you help me pick up all my scattered trash.
Oh dear...I promise to pick them up for you.
Sarah: *sniffs* Alright then...It went northeast.
Sarah: Make sure to give all the paper to my dad, Jack after collecting all the paper. I'm sure you've met him.
